title: Keira Maguire attends the Fudge Clean Blonde launch in Sydney
text:
She's the former Bachelor star known for her enviably toned physique.

And on Thursday, Keira Maguire showed off her sensational frame as she attended the Fudge Clean Blonde launch in Sydney.

The 33-year-old dressed to impress as she flaunted her busty assets in a denim mini dress with a plunging neckline.

Dare to bare! Keira Maguire (pictured) flaunted her busty assets and endless pins in a denim mini dress as she attended the Fudge Clean Blonde launch on Thursday

Flaunt it! Keira (pictured) showed off her sensational frame in a denim mini dress complete with a plunging neckline

She accessorised her look with a pair of black strappy heels, a mini purse and a pair of hoop earrings.

Keira styled her signature golden locks in simple waves which fell effortlessly by her shoulders.

The blonde beauty wore a striking make-up palette consisting of black eyeliner, a nude lip and faux lashes.

Accessories: The Bachelor star completed her look with a pair of black strappy heels and a mini purse

After arriving to the event, Keira posed alongside model Madi Edwards who flaunted her petite physique in a black figure-hugging dress.

Madi accessorised her ensemble with a pair of white sneakers, a black bag, statement earrings and white pearl hair clips.

She let her natural beauty shine opting for minimal make-up and left her blonde locks out.

All smiles: Keira styled her signature golden locks in simple waves which fell effortlessly by her shoulders

Glow: The 33-year-old wore a striking make-up palette consisting of black eyeliner, a nude lip and faux lashes

Keira rose to fame in 2016 after failing to find love with Richie Strahan on the fourth season of The Bachelor.

She then appeared on Bachelor In Paradise in 2017 where she found love with Jarrod Woodgate.

In August, Keira confirmed she'd split from Jarrod just months after they'd rekindled their relationship following a split last year.

Strike a pose: Keira (left) posed alongside model Madi Edwards (right) who flaunted her petite physique in a black figure-hugging dress

Statement: Madi (pictured) accessorised her ensemble with a pair of white sneakers, a black bag and statement earrings
